location.fullValue: The Sydney Plan, Falcon Meadows at Bent Grass

data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom home built with meticulous attention to detail in 2022. Located in the desirable bent grass neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The home features gas in the kitchen with a large breakfast bar. Luxury   Vinal Planking thought out the home.  3 spacious bedrooms on the upper level. The master bathroom features double sinks a large walk-in closet and modern walk-in shower. On the lower level you will find a great use of space, a large office area with access from the garage or front door. This home is loved and cared for, with tasteful upgrading done.
